---
items:
  - "alpha"
  - "bravo"
  - "charlie"
admin: true
---

Without trimming, whitespace is preserved:
{{ for item in items }}
  {{ item }}
{{ /for }}
---
Compact list with full trim:
[{{- for item in items -}}({{- item -}}){{- /for -}}]
---
Trim outer tags only:
{{- for item in items }}
  * {{ item }}
{{ /for -}}
---
For inside trimmed if:
{{- if admin -}}
{{- for item in items }}
  [{{ item }}]
{{ /for -}}
{{- /if -}}
---
Nested context:
Start
{{- for item in items -}}
[{{ item }}]
{{- /for -}}
End